  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" width="100%"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">A harrier is a sort of hawk that flies low to the ground and attempts to eat the small rodents and other animals that live under rocks and in holes.  Now that you know this, you can put the whole thing in perspective.  An Aviak Harrier is a ... well ... it harries things.  Killing a few will give you a bad standing with the Aviaks, who don't really appreciate having citizens killed off by wandering cutthroats such as yourself.</font></td>
